785
01:53:09.991 --> 01:53:10.889
sweet-like...

786
01:53:53.371 --> 01:53:54.963
Lot of good men died here. Riddick.

787
01:53:55.740 --> 01:53:59.141
Not sure how I'm supposed
to overlook that. Next time.

788
01:53:59.978 --> 01:54:01.809
Yeah. Things would
have been different

789
