791
01:54:09.955 --> 01:54:13.891
You know what? Fuck that. Don't tell me.
I don't wanna know.

792
01:54:14.727 --> 01:54:16.718
I'll tell you this. Johns.

793
01:54:17.096 --> 01:54:20.260
Sooner or later.
we all have to head home.

794
01:54:21.301 --> 01:54:23.394
Tell Dahl to keep it warm for me.

795
01:54:24.337 --> 01:54:25.634
And Johns...

